data.description: Welcome to this 3 bedroom ranch home, nestled on a quiet Cul-de-sac close to schools, shopping, Highway. 3 spacious bedrooms on the main floor. Original wood floors throughout. With over 1300 sf of living space there's plenty of room to relax. This home offers an eat in kitchen with lots of cabinets and a full size basement with ample storage. Large living room at the front of the home with a picture window that was replaced in 2020 and offers plenty of natural light along with a wood burning fireplace. Updates include New roof 2023, furnace and A/C 2016. Stove, refrigerator, washer and dryer included. Seller is including a 1 year home warranty.
